predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareNoiDeLaUltimulLogin: (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}') AND (DOSARE.DATA_CREARE >= '{1}' OR '{1}' IS NULL)
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareNeoperate: (((DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI <= '{1}') OR (DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE <= '{1}') OR (DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE IS NULL)) AND (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO = {0} OR (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA = {0} AND UPPER(DOSARE.STATUS) NOT IN ('INCOMPLET','NEAVIZAT'))))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareCascoNeoperate: (((DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI <= '{1}') OR (DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE <= '{1}') OR (DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE IS NULL)) AND DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO = {0})
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareRcaNeoperate: (((DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI <= '{1}') OR (DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE <= '{1}') OR (DOSARE.DATA_ULTIMEI_MODIFICARI IS NULL AND DOSARE.DATA_CREARE IS NULL)) AND (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA = {0} AND UPPER(DOSARE.STATUS) NOT IN ('INCOMPLET','NEAVIZAT')))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareNeasignate: ((DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}') AND DOSARE.ID NOT IN (SELECT ID_DOSAR FROM UTILIZATORI_DOSARE))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareCascoNeasignate: (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' AND DOSARE.ID NOT IN (SELECT ID_DOSAR FROM UTILIZATORI_DOSARE))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareRcaNeasignate: (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}' AND DOSARE.ID NOT IN (SELECT ID_DOSAR FROM UTILIZATORI_DOSARE))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareNeasignateFromLastLogin: ((DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}') AND DOSARE.ID NOT IN (SELECT ID_DOSAR FROM UTILIZATORI_DOSARE) AND (DOSARE.DATA_CREARE >= '{1}' OR '{1}' IS NULL))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareCascoNeasignateFromLastLogin: (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' AND DOSARE.ID NOT IN (SELECT ID_DOSAR FROM UTILIZATORI_DOSARE) AND (DOSARE.DATA_CREARE >= '{1}' OR '{1}' IS NULL))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareRcaNeasignateFromLastLogin: (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}' AND DOSARE.ID NOT IN (SELECT ID_DOSAR FROM UTILIZATORI_DOSARE) AND (DOSARE.DATA_CREARE >= '{1}' OR '{1}' IS NULL))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareAvizateTotal: (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}') AND DOSARE.STATUS NOT IN ('INCOMPLET','NEAVIZAT')
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareAvizateNeexpediate: DOSARE.STATUS NOT IN ('INCOMPLET', 'NEAVIZAT') AND (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}') AND DOSARE.ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT ID_DOSAR FROM CLICK_COUNT WHERE UPPER(OPERATION)='EMAIL CERERE' AND COUNTER>0)
predefinedDashboardFilters.proceseTotal: ((PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NOT NULL AND (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}')) OR (PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NULL AND (PROCESE.ID_RECLAMANT='{0}' OR PROCESE.ID_PARAT='{0}')))
predefinedDashboardFilters.proceseReclamantTotal: ((PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}') OR (PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NULL AND PROCESE.ID_RECLAMANT='{0}'))
predefinedDashboardFilters.proceseParatTotal: ((PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NOT NULL AND DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}') OR (PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NULL AND PROCESE.ID_PARAT='{0}'))
predefinedDashboardFilters.proceseNoiTotal: (LOWER(S.DENUMIRE) = 'preluat de la asigurator' AND ((PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NOT NULL AND (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}')) OR (PROCESE.ID_DOSAR IS NULL AND (PROCESE.ID_RECLAMANT='{0}' OR PROCESE.ID_PARAT='{0}'))))
predefinedDashboardFilters.dosareFaraProces: (DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_CASCO='{0}' OR DOSARE.ID_SOCIETATE_RCA='{0}') AND (IFNULL(DOSARE.`COUNT_PROCESE`, 0) = 0 AND D.INSTANTA = TRUE)
